@startuml usds_justice40-tool

actor User
participant "Client Application" as Client
participant "Data Pipeline" as Pipeline
database "S3 Data Lake" as S3
participant "ETL Processes" as ETL
participant "Scoring Module" as Scoring
participant "Map Tile Generator" as TileGen
participant "External Data Sources" as DataSources

User -> Client: Interacts with map/UI
Client -> S3: Fetch map tiles and data

Pipeline -> DataSources: Extract raw data
DataSources --> Pipeline: Raw data
Pipeline -> ETL: Process data
ETL -> S3: Store processed data
Pipeline -> Scoring: Calculate Justice40 scores
Scoring -> S3: Store scores
Pipeline -> TileGen: Generate map tiles
TileGen -> S3: Store map tiles

Client -> S3: Request updated data
S3 --> Client: Provide updated data
Client -> User: Display updated information

@enduml